CREATE VIEW [business_rules].[xmldelivery_s_xmlinterface]
AS

  SELECT 
    bo.[business key for hub xmldelivery],                                         -- Business Key for Hub XMLDelivery
    bo.[ps xmldelivery - xmlinterface - default of vi_xml_delivery_u_staging],     -- Entry Present in Satellite XMLDelivery > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_DELIVERY_U_STAGING
    bo.[lts xmldelivery - xmlinterface - default of vi_xml_delivery_u_staging],    -- Load Time Satellite XMLDelivery > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_DELIVERY_U_STAGING
    bo.[updated],                                                                  -- [updated] from Satellite XMLDelivery > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_DELIVERY_U_STAGING
    bo.[delivery_guid],                                                            -- [delivery_guid] from Satellite XMLDelivery > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_DELIVERY_U_STAGING
    bo.[delivery_cbdnumber],                                                       -- [delivery_cbdnumber] from Satellite XMLDelivery > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_DELIVERY_U_STAGING
    bo.[delivery_revisionalm],                                                     -- [delivery_revisionalm] from Satellite XMLDelivery > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_DELIVERY_U_STAGING
    bo.[delivery_title],                                                           -- [delivery_title] from Satellite XMLDelivery > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_DELIVERY_U_STAGING
    bo.[delivery_customer],                                                        -- [delivery_customer] from Satellite XMLDelivery > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_DELIVERY_U_STAGING
    bo.[delivery_delivereddate],                                                   -- [delivery_delivereddate] from Satellite XMLDelivery > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_DELIVERY_U_STAGING
    bo.[delivery_deliverytype],                                                    -- [delivery_deliverytype] from Satellite XMLDelivery > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_DELIVERY_U_STAGING
    bo.[delivery_deliverynumber],                                                  -- [delivery_deliverynumber] from Satellite XMLDelivery > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_DELIVERY_U_STAGING
    bo.[delivery_ecuname],                                                         -- [delivery_ecuname] from Satellite XMLDelivery > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_DELIVERY_U_STAGING
    bo.[delivery_indbdate],                                                        -- [delivery_indbdate] from Satellite XMLDelivery > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_DELIVERY_U_STAGING
    bo.[delivery_producttitle],                                                    -- [delivery_producttitle] from Satellite XMLDelivery > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_DELIVERY_U_STAGING
    bo.[delivery_programtitle],                                                    -- [delivery_programtitle] from Satellite XMLDelivery > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_DELIVERY_U_STAGING
    bo.[delivery_reltype],                                                         -- [delivery_reltype] from Satellite XMLDelivery > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_DELIVERY_U_STAGING
    bo.[delivery_bisbeta],                                                         -- [delivery_bisbeta] from Satellite XMLDelivery > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_DELIVERY_U_STAGING
    bo.[delivery_bissafetyrelevantc],                                              -- [delivery_bissafetyrelevantc] from Satellite XMLDelivery > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_DELIVERY_U_STAGING
    bo.[delivery_testedderivate],                                                  -- [delivery_testedderivate] from Satellite XMLDelivery > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_DELIVERY_U_STAGING
    bo.[component_name],                                                           -- [component_name] from Satellite XMLDelivery > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_DELIVERY_U_STAGING
    bo.[component_version]                                                         -- [component_version] from Satellite XMLDelivery > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_DELIVERY_U_STAGING

  FROM [businessobjects].[xmldelivery_s_xmlinterface] AS bo
;
